Module kivakit.core.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.interfaces.messaging

Interface Transmittable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Message
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Activity, Alert, Announcement, CompressibleCollection.CompressionEvent, CriticalAlert, Failure, Incomplete, Information, Narration, OperationFailed, OperationHalted, OperationLifecycleMessage, OperationMessage, OperationStarted, OperationStatusMessage, OperationSucceeded, Problem, Quibble, Success, Trace, Unsupported, ValidationProblem, Warning
    public interface Transmittable
    A message object that can be transmitted with a Broadcaster and received by a Listener. Although Message is the primary implementor Transmittable any class can implement this interface and participate in the broadcaster / listener framework.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
